title: Build with me: Overpowered AMD PC, 10 Gbps M.2 NVMe?
description:
Come build with me! I'm building a massively overspec'd workshop PC so I can test out a new 10 Gbps M.2 NIC that slots into one of my motherboard's M.2 slots.

Also because it's been a while since I did a live stream, and I thought it would be fun to do one again—feel free to ask any questions in chat while we hang out! Should I boot Windows? Linux? You decide!
